                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<h3>How to Track Your Order</h3><p>Once your order has been dispatched from our workshop in Dongguan, China, you will receive a <strong>shipping confirmation email</strong> with your tracking details (if tracking is available for your chosen shipping method).</p><p>To check the status of your order at any time:</p><ul><li><strong>Check your email</strong> - Look for a shipping confirmation from SiconArt with your tracking number and carrier link.</li><li><strong>Click the tracking link</strong> - Follow the link in your email to view real-time updates from the shipping carrier.</li><li><strong>Contact us directly</strong> - If you cannot find your tracking information or need an update, email us and we will look it up for you.</li></ul>",
