                        {
                            "elType": "widget",
                            "widgetType": "text-editor",
                            "settings": {
                                "editor": "<h3>Estimated Delivery Times</h3><p>All orders ship from Dongguan, China. Delivery times vary by destination and shipping method selected at checkout. Please allow additional time for customs clearance in your country.</p><p>For detailed shipping information, please see our <a href='/shipping-policy/'>Shipping Policy</a>.</p><h3>Common Tracking Questions</h3><p><strong>My tracking hasn't updated in several days.</strong><br>International shipments may show gaps in tracking updates, especially during customs processing. This is normal. If there is no update for more than 14 business days, contact us and we will investigate with the carrier.</p><p><strong>My tracking shows delivered but I haven't received it.</strong><br>Please check with household members, neighbours, or your local post office. If the package is still missing after 48 hours, email us with your order number and we will open an investigation.</p><p><strong>I didn't receive a tracking number.</strong><br>Not all shipping methods include tracking. If you selected a tracked option and haven't received details within 5 business days of your order, email us at <strong>support@siconart.com</strong> and we will follow up.</p>",
